      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**AEGIS Forecast Drift — Volatility** · Governed read-only **V2** snapshot via datasource `aegis-forecast-drift-csv`. Rolling dispersion / oscillation / sign-change behavior (`volatility_drift_score`, governed family weight **10%**). **Partial computability:** **144 / 168** signals are computable (**coverage 85.7 %**); the **24** non-computable signals are governed by `not_computable_reason = INSUFFICIENT_VERSIONS` (first two versions of each key). Governed auxiliary metrics (`rolling_stddev`, `rolling_cov`, `rolling_mad`, `oscillation_count`, `sign_change_freq`, `volatility_class`) come from the family-scores table (keyed by Forecast Key + Forecast Version). KPIs, ranking and the signal details table honor all five shared filters; the drift trend ignores Forecast Version to keep the full historical series."
      }
    },
